    <briefdescription>
<para>Accumulated metrics for a single move/trajectory. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Updated every update() call. Read back after a move completes to evaluate tracking performance without storing per-sample data. Call <ref refid="syn__motor__ctrl_8c_1ad22aaf542cd734f0c86e4fb0901e413b" kindref="member">syn_motor_ctrl_reset_metrics()</ref> before a move to start fresh. </para>
